							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="Debate"><strong>MOTIONS</strong></p><p class="SubDebate"><strong>Misuse of Drugs Act 1975—</strong><strong>Approval of Order</strong></p><p class="Speech"><a name="time_20160912 15:04:38" ></a><strong>Hon PETER DUNNE (Associate Minister of Health)</strong>: I move, <em>That, pursuant to section 4A of the Misuse of Drugs Act 1975, this House approve the Misuse of Drugs (Classification and Presumption of Supply—25B-NBOMe, 25C-NBOMe, and 251-NBOMe) Order 2016, made under section 4 of that Act.</em></p><p class="IndentMarginalone">Motion agreed to.</p></div></body>
