							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="VoteReason">A party vote was called for on the question,<em> That the </em><em>Child Protection (Child Sex Offender Government Agency Registration) Bill be now read a third time</em><em>.</em></p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Ayes 107</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand National 59; New Zealand Labour 32; New Zealand First 12; Māori Party 2; ACT New Zealand 1; United Future 1.</p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Noes 14</strong></p><p class="VoteText">Green Party 14.</p><p class="VoteResult">Motion agreed to.</p><p class="IndentMarginalone">Bill read a third time.</p></div></body>
